Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:29.62,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:32.85,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:36.67,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思うまま書き滑らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:41.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}描く未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}澄み渡る空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:53.72,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}果てしないほど青く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:57.74,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邪気な心に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:02:01.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充たされ魅かれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:05.30,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて自由に飛びまわれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:08.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}翼を手に入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:12.84,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無垢な瞳は求めてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:16.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}空の向こうへ　行きたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:19.74,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}止め処ない願いから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:23.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一つだけ叶うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:26.83,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰にも譲りたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:30.83,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夢を掴みたいと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:34.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:37.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:41.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつまでも描き続けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:46.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}願う未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:29.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童时的那个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:32.85,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:36.67,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}随心所欲地去描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:41.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己描绘的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}万里无云的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:53.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无边无际的蔚蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:57.74,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}纯洁无瑕的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:02:01.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充盈着无限魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:05.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}终于能自由翱翔于天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:08.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}长出了美丽的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:12.84,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无瑕的瞳孔在寻求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:16.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想去那天空的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:19.74,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在那无数的愿望中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:23.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}若是只有一个能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:26.83,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不愿让给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:30.83,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要紧紧抓住那梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:34.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童时的那个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:37.31,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:41.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}永不停息地去描写
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:46.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己祈愿的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.43,0:23:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,780)\fad(1000,8)\3a&00&\3c&0000A0&}诀别
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:43.20,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}炎さえも凍てついた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:49.86,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独の中求む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:58.52,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}魂から結びつき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.74,0:22:06.55,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私を恋い暖めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:15.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　祈りの言葉がふるえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:23.08,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　弱きいのちが消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:30.95,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえす　輪廻の流れ辿り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:39.57,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終わらない世界の宿命を見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:47.07,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえし　詠われる者達よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:55.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}守られてまどろむ宵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:43.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就算火焰都冻结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:49.86,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}也在孤独中寻求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:58.52,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}请用灵魂连结我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.74,0:22:06.55,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}请用爱恋温暖我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:15.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}呜呼 那颤抖的祈愿之声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:23.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}呜呼 那脆弱的生命消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:30.95,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}追溯那不断交替的轮回之流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:39.57,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}凝望那永不终结的世界的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:47.07,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不断轮回的 那些传颂之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:55.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}被守护着安眠的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快点走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.71,0:00:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.94,0:00:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们卡露拉阿滋雷的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯欧卡斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.17,0:01:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运送剑奴的货船
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到叛乱军的袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.14,0:01:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑奴都被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上开始准备讨伐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.85,0:01:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经做好迎接你的准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请快点来到我的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阿露 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有讨厌吃的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 没有这事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 东霞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面没有下毒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 给圣上的食物一定要先由在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝纳威大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎在纳·托库的剑奴发动了叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳·托库
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得那里应该是卡露拉原先所在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率领叛乱军的似乎是一个叫做迪利霍莱的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于物资的严重不足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛乱军渐渐开始处于劣势
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事相求 所以来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿了不同的衣服给人的感觉也不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有事相求 穿正装也是基本的礼仪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳·托库吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入正题真快呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话我也想帮点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会因此而让这个国家卷入战火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 我不会自私到要你白白帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我的一切都奉献给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 从每一根发丝到每一滴血
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及我的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,订立「解放者」的契约
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己在说些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我让你去死的话你真的会去死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是主人的愿望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有这样的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就实现你的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约看来成立了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 和这个倒没什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想白白接受恩惠哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我说过了身心都要奉献给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了 哈克奥罗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露 能倒点茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉最近艾露露好像一直躲着我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那您心里有没有数呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总大将
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克罗 情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 情况不容乐观
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在叛乱军节节败退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被镇压应该只是时间上的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 你可以退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉 正如你所听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再进一步的介入恐怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 身体不能动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 已经醒来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉 这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微去旅行一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳·托库吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上是需要安静的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是要走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你察觉到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉 我是这个国家的国师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能理解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下总算得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这个时间了 在干些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去旅行哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 请稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这回事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在玩什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去旅行哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小柚 小神 也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起旅行 真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让在下也同行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 随你们便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚叶！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝纳威 柚叶她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他逃了…让他逃了…让他逃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他逃了…让他逃了…让他逃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉 过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好天气呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是啊…没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的山…真高呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地…地面…真是凹凸不平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个只是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我…误会什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上 卡露拉拜托我支援纳·托库的叛乱军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有一点强迫性质
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过既没做过什么 也没被怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…但是…我并不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让重要的人就这样产生误会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 艾露露对于我来说是重要的家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆库鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露 到里面去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 东霞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是迪利霍莱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是统率叛乱军「卡露拉阿滋雷」的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉阿滋雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是靠打仗维持生计的旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这里发生了战事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想请您雇佣我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是雇佣兵么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是我们的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有来历不明的人插手的份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的弟弟说了不需要我们的帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不否定啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来者何人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的 东霞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 卡托玛乌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是卡露拉阿滋雷大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遵守约定了呢 把那孩子抚养到这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢夸奖 我愧不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 也要把这件事告诉迪利霍莱大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫卡露拉阿滋雷的女人已经不存在于这个世上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我只是一个名叫卡露拉的 普通的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我杀 一个都别放过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这里会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照约定…请让我见妻儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 让你们见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去见在黄泉等着你的妻儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤…撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔姆 振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡托玛乌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…只是…想和妻儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是背叛者应有的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…面对死者为何还要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 对不起 手滑了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小男人一个 被人背叛是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有站在弱者的立场上考虑过事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 身为吉利亚基纳族的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs48\fsp-1}注：吉利亚基纳族：战斗能力十分突出的种族。拥有为了战斗而强化的身体，\N没有固定的战斗方式也是其特征。曾经一度繁荣，但是现在只有少数幸存者了。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要站在弱者的立场上考虑事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉利亚基纳族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个因为依仗着强大而不知体会弱者痛苦的傲慢一族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是因此招致灭亡的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 即便你是末裔 但也是吉利亚基纳族的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允许你再这样侮辱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 看来再和你多说什么你也明白不了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就让你亲身体会一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为弱者的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣 居然说要和我迪利霍莱交手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 为什么不摆架势
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是什么都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉利亚基纳族人是不需要什么架势的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉…不 各位旅行中的佣兵阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必助我们一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡托玛乌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己站得起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪利霍莱大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于回到我的身边了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深爱的人


